## ⚡ Speed Comparison

| Items | Old Time | New Time | You Save |
|-------|----------|----------|----------|
| 1     | 30 sec   | 30 sec   | 0 sec    |
| 5     | 150 sec  | 70 sec   | 80 sec   |
| 10    | 300 sec  | 120 sec  | 180 sec  |

**For 10 items: Save 3 minutes! (60% faster)**

---

## 🎮 Controls Quick Reference

### After Save Button:
- ✅ **Challan**: Kept same
- ✅ **Party**: Kept same
- ❌ **Item**: Cleared → **Cursor here!**
- 📅 **Dates**: Auto-filled with today

### Keyboard Shortcut:
```
1. Click Save (or Alt+S)
2. Type item name → dropdown filters
3. Press ↓ arrow → select item
4. Press Enter
5. Tab to Qty
6. Enter quantity
7. Repeat from step 1
```

---

## 🆚 Button Comparison

| Button | Challan | Party | Item | When to Use |
|--------|---------|-------|------|-------------|
| **SAVE** | ✓ Keep | ✓ Keep | ✗ Clear | Same challan, different items |
| **NEW** | ✗ Clear | ✓ Keep | ✓ Keep | New challan, same party |
| **CLEAR** | ✗ Clear | ✗ Clear | ✗ Clear | Fresh start |

---

## ✅ Auto-Filled Fields

When adding new record:
- 📅 **Date**: Today (can change)
- 📅 **Bill Date**: Today (can change)
- 🏭 **Used in Machine**: Empty (optional)
- 👤 **Taken By**: Empty (optional)

