## 📊 Real-World Example

**Scenario**: Morning delivery from ABC Steel

```
Challan: CH-2024-001
Party: ABC Steel Industries

Items:
1. Steel Plates 10mm - 50 pcs   → 30 sec (full entry)
2. Steel Rods 12mm - 100 pcs    → 10 sec (quick)
3. Angles L50 - 75 pcs          → 10 sec (quick)
4. Bolts M12 - 500 pcs          → 10 sec (quick)
5. Nuts M12 - 500 pcs           → 10 sec (quick)

Total: 70 seconds
Old way: 150 seconds
Saved: 80 seconds (53% faster!)
```

